Looking at this misconfiguration, the rule CKV2_AWS_33 requires AppSync GraphQL APIs to be protected by WAF. The affected resource is `aws_appsync_graphql_api.all` (lines 3-11).

To fix this, I need to associate a WAF Web ACL with the AppSync GraphQL API using `aws_wafv2_web_acl_association`. The resource ARN for AppSync follows the pattern used with WAF associations.

I'll add a WAF Web ACL resource and associate it with the `aws_appsync_graphql_api.all` resource to fix the violation.

```json
